OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Flingering showers moving away
OL,7,Fsoutheastwards during the evening,
OL,8,Fthen a dry night with clear spells.
OL,9,FOvernight temperatures rather fresher
OL,10,Fthan of late in western parts,
OL,11,Fespecially in rural spots. Light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FDry with hazy sunshine and
OL,14,Fvery warm or hot for many again on
OL,15,FSaturday. Cooler near eastern coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
